FBIS4-18952 "drweu070_l_94002" FBIS-WEU-94-070 Daily Report 11 Apr 1994 SPAIN Further Reportage on Russian President's Visit Further Reportage on Russian President's Visit King Juan Carlos Welcomes Yeltsin LD1104112794 Madrid TVE Internacional Television in Spanish 1030 GMT 11 Apr 94 LD1104112794 Madrid TVE Internacional Television Spanish BFN [Text] Boris Yeltsin arrived at Barajas airport at midday, and shortly afterward he was officially welcomed at the El Pardo Palace by the King and Queen of Spain, don Juan Carlos and dona Sofia. The political transition in Spain interests Yeltsin, who is going through a difficult time in his country, where his struggle with important sectors of the parliament continues.
